        "action": "Eject US Armed Forces personnel from bases hosted by UK & apply to join BRICS",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "We call on the Government to eject all US Armed Forces personnel from bases in the UK and apply to join the BRIC (Brazil, Russia, India, China) foreign investment strategies grouping. We believe that Britain has been in the economic grip of America for too long.",
